dct_title_s: Georgien = Georgia = Géorgie = Гру́зия / Reise Know-How. (Western Georgia)
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours, gradient tints, and spot heights. Depth shown by bathymetric tints and isolines. Road map with tourist features. Panel title. "Rip & waterproof." Includes index to place names, location map, color illustrations, and publisher's advertisement. Legend includes roads, railways, national parks, district boundaries, mountains, places of interest, and passes. Legend in English, French, Spanish, and Russian.
